{"tid":2277511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"晒毛澤東遭掌摑照　宇宙少女延靜被轟涉辱華","createTime":"2020-11-08T13:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T13:40:32.000Z","uid":21141,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"530863b8765379d6c713aaed1648f117a7c4dbd5","tid":2277511,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"韓團宇宙少女的21歲成員俞延靜近日被內地網民發現她於今年8月，曾在社交網上傳到首爾一家咖啡店，並在店內打卡的照片，當時她手上還拿着與私交甚篤的女團TWICE成員Sana的合照，2人疑一起到訪該店。而內地網民發現延靜打卡的照片中，牆上掛着毛澤東臉上滿布掌印的藝術照，看起來似是毛澤東遭人掌摑一樣。<br />\n不少內地網民不堪畫中的毛澤東受辱，即在延靜的社交網上留言炮轟她涉辱華，連帶跟她一起合照的Sana亦慘被拖落水，同樣遭內地網民抨擊，而在惹起爭議後，延靜已將相關照片刪除<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awB2bHw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawB2bHw.png&h=44e59e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AKBmsfS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAKBmsfS.png&h=00674489&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5P7nPe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5P7nPe.png&h=58c8d4c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mnYPA9N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmnYPA9N.png&h=f180e22b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}